text: Pseudostixis flavifrons is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Aurivillis in 1914, originally under the genus Stixis.BioLib.cz - Pseudostixis flavifrons. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1914
title: Pseudostixis flavifrons
